OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a mostly cloudy day
OL,6,Fwith patchy rain developing at times,
OL,7,Fmainly over western areas. The cloud
OL,8,Fmay break up in the afternoon to allow
OL,9,Fsunnier skies for southeast England
OL,10,Fand eastern Scotland. Feeling rather
OL,11,Fmild in sunshine.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRemaining mostly cloudy
OL,14,Fovernight and turning rather murky
OL,15,Ftoo, especially in the south and east.
OL,16,FPatchy rain arriving over Northern
OL,17,FIreland and western Scotland by
OL,18,Fmorning. A mostly mild night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
