OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FCloudy again for most, rain
OL,6,Fin the west slowly moving east and
OL,7,Fweakening. Winds increasing through
OL,8,Fthe day, breaking up the cloud.
OL,9,FFurther rain arriving in the west by
OL,10,Fevening.
